        Alarm object.
        参数:
        year - the alarm time of year.
        mon - the alarm time of mon.
        day - the alarm time of day.
        hour - the alarm time of hour.
        min - the alarm time of min.
        id - the alarm id.
        dayflags - the repetition flag
